{
  "stem": "490.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And today, we think of it as a prayer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If we talk about-- and a high power takes-- watches over us, or whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But sometimes, when you live your life and you see things happen that-- nobody has control over it, except, you think, yourself, and you know you are very helpless.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you feel that you're never-- never alone, and this was my strength when I was a youngster, too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I really had nobody except my feelings, that my-- conviction that somebody is guiding me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've never-- I haven't mentioned-- when I was born-- which it was-- I already had-- my father remarried my mother.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- my father had a son and a daughter from his previous marriage.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, all of a sudden, I remember when I was four that my brother was already married.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was around 20 years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my sister, which it was a half-sister-- she was maybe a year younger or maybe two years younger.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it's a matter of fact, when I-- when my mother died, when I was three months old, because she had pneumonia.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in Poland it was a deadly disease, if you don't-- even for young people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my sister raised me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, it was-- the father left the house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- and my sister and them-- my half-sister and brother, they lived in this house, and his family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I would say that my sister raised me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when I left this house, when I left Luboml, I lost all connections with my brother, because my brother was not exactly very happy that I left home.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He thought I would stay and help him with his work or whatever his business was.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
